
                                   full_nohz
                                  -----------

1. Introduction
----------------

Enable full dynticks system for nohz.

If you need more details, Please see linux/Documnetation/timers/NO_HZ.txt.

2. Usage
--------

Add this template using the following configure script option.
i.e.: --templates feature/full_nohz

This will ensure the required kernel config values are set. 
